224
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:40,919
Okay.

225
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,340
So that's another great phrase.

226
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:44,580
You show some respect.

227
00:10:45,139 --> 00:10:45,259
All right.

228
00:10:45,259 --> 00:10:49,100
So the key here is that this is, the verb is to show, right?

229
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:49,700
Not to give.

230
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:52,000
